<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 09:13:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特斯拉 6 月中国制造电动汽车销量同比下降 24.2%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-june-china-made-ev-sales-down-242-yy-2024-07-02/</link><description>中国乘用车协会(CPCA)周二的数据显示，特斯拉6月份中国制造的电动汽车销量同比下降24.2%至71,007辆。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 09:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-june-china-made-ev-sales-down-242-yy-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国和澳大利亚在太平洋影响力竞赛中捐赠建筑物和机场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-australia-donate-buildings-airstrips-pacific-influence-race-2024-07-02/</link><description>中国在瓦努阿图捐赠了一座总统大楼，澳大利亚和新西兰则在邻国所罗门群岛斥资 5500 万澳元落成机场，以争夺在太平洋岛屿地区的影响力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 08:58:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-australia-donate-buildings-airstrips-pacific-influence-race-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>律师称，外国法官之争损害了香港商法中心的吸引力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-commercial-law-hub-allure-damaged-by-foreign-judges-row-lawyers-say-2024-07-02/</link><description>一些律师和专家表示，中国统治的香港最高法院两名英国法官的辞职不仅引发了人们对法治的担忧，还将进一步削弱人们对香港更广泛的商业法律部门的信心。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 06:04:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-commercial-law-hub-allure-damaged-by-foreign-judges-row-lawyers-say-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪电动汽车季度销量增长 21%，缩小与特斯拉的差距</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-posts-21-jump-quarterly-ev-sales-closes-gap-with-tesla-2024-07-02/</link><description>中国比亚迪第二季度电动汽车销量增长 21%，在第一季度将全球最大电动汽车供应商头衔拱手让给美国竞争对手特斯拉后，缩小了与特斯拉的差距。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 05:06:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-posts-21-jump-quarterly-ev-sales-closes-gap-with-tesla-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>解说：中国计划制定的金融稳定法是什么？它将如何运作？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/what-is-chinas-planned-financial-stability-law-how-will-it-work-2024-07-02/</link><description>中国即将公布其金融稳定法，其中包括设立一个基金来救助陷入困境的金融机构，这是北京为防止世界第二大经济体发生系统性金融风险而采取的更广泛努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 04:57:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/what-is-chinas-planned-financial-stability-law-how-will-it-work-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>大型开发商销售降幅收窄后，中国房地产企业大幅上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-property-firms-jump-after-big-developers-show-smaller-sales-drop-2024-07-02/</link><description>私人数据显示，6 月份中国主要房地产开发商的销售额跌幅继续收窄，周二在香港上市的中国房地产公司股价大幅上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 04:29:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-property-firms-jump-after-big-developers-show-smaller-sales-drop-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>梵蒂冈呼吁和平解决包括南海争端在内的冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-june-17-south-china-sea-incident-most-aggressive-recent-chinese-2024-07-02/</link><description>梵蒂冈周二呼吁和平解决冲突，包括菲律宾和中国之间的紧张局势，因为两国正在努力解决南海争端。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 04:26:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-june-17-south-china-sea-incident-most-aggressive-recent-chinese-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>印尼协会称中国球员张因心脏骤停去世</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/chinese-player-zhang-died-cardiac-arrest-indonesia-association-says-2024-07-02/</link><description>印度尼西亚羽毛球协会（PBSI）表示，17岁的中国运动员张志杰在周日的一场比赛中倒地后因心脏骤停死亡。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 03:26:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/chinese-player-zhang-died-cardiac-arrest-indonesia-association-says-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>微软整合中国零售渠道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-consolidates-retail-channels-china-2024-07-02/</link><description>微软正在整合其在中国大陆的零售渠道，该公司在回应媒体报道称其将关闭其在全球第二大经济体的授权实体零售商网络时表示。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 01:52:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/microsoft-consolidates-retail-channels-china-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国称美国瞄准人工智能无助于健康发展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/china-says-us-targeting-ai-not-helpful-healthy-development-2024-07-01/</link><description>中国驻联合国特使周一表示，美国针对中国人工智能的某些投资无助于人工智能技术的“健康发展”，并且在全球治理方面将产生分歧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 21:58:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/china-says-us-targeting-ai-not-helpful-healthy-development-2024-07-01/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉在第二季度交付报告发布前上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-rises-ahead-q2-deliveries-report-2024-07-01/</link><description>特斯拉股价周一上涨近 6%，此前一家重要的华尔街券商在特斯拉周二发布季度生产和交付报告之前将该股列入观察名单。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 17:45:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-rises-ahead-q2-deliveries-report-2024-07-01/</guid></item><item><title>雷诺电动汽车部门 Ampere 与 LGES、CATL 合作开发电池技术</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/renaults-ev-unit-ampere-bet-lfp-technology-ev-batteries-2024-07-01/</link><description>雷诺旗下电动汽车部门 Ampere 周一表示，将在其电动汽车量产计划中纳入磷酸铁锂 (LFP) 技术，并与 LG Energy Solution (LGES) 和 CATL 合作，在欧洲建立供应链。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 15:55:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/renaults-ev-unit-ampere-bet-lfp-technology-ev-batteries-2024-07-01/</guid></item><item><title>Chess-Ding vs Gukesh 世界冠军赛将在新加坡举行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/chess-ding-v-gukesh-world-championship-match-take-place-singapore-2024-07-01/</link><description>国际象棋联合会（FIDE）周一表示，印度古克什·D·D和卫冕冠军中国选手丁立人之间的经典国际象棋世界冠军赛将于11月20日至12月15日在新加坡举行。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 12:39:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/chess-ding-v-gukesh-world-championship-match-take-place-singapore-2024-07-01/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜将电视转播从中国转至俄罗斯卫星</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-switches-tv-transmission-russia-satellite-chinese-2024-07-01/</link><description>韩国统一部周一表示，朝鲜已将国家电视广播的传输从中国卫星改为俄罗斯卫星，这使得对此类广播的监控对韩国政府机构和媒体构成挑战。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 09:12:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-switches-tv-transmission-russia-satellite-chinese-2024-07-01/</guid></item><item><title>中国向香港、澳门永久居民提供五年签证</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-offers-foreign-permanent-residents-hong-kong-macau-five-year-visas-2024-07-01/</link><description>中国国家移民管理局周一表示，前往中国大陆的香港和澳门永久居民的外国人可以申请有效期五年的多次入境旅游签证。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 06:50:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-offers-foreign-permanent-residents-hong-kong-macau-five-year-visas-2024-07-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>